---
headline: "Design vision, <span>technological craft</span>"
section: "index"
---

<section class="intro">
	<div class="content-block">
		<p>Traversing the realms of art direction, visual identity, print, and interactive, for over 20 years I’ve been solving problems at the intersection of design and code. I am currently available for hire, remotely or on site in Atlanta.</p>
	</div>
</section>
<section id="portfolio" class="portfolio-list design-portfolio-list">
	<h2>Portfolio</h2>
	<%= partial '/partials/portfolio_list' %>
</section>
<section class="portfolio-list code-sample-list">
	<h2>Code samples</h2>
